data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT !   Welcome to this meticulously maintained  Brick Cape Cod located in the beautiful neighborhood of the Connecticut Avenue Estates of Silver Spring, boasting 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a bonus room, and a fully finished basement. Step inside to discover an inviting open living and dining area adorned with original hardwood floors, freshly painted throughout. The kitchen showcases sleek granite countertops, an eye-catching backsplash, and stainless steel appliances.  The basement offers a second kitchen, full bathroom, one bedroom, a second room that could be turned into an office or another bedroom, and a full size washer and dryer.  The basement has a private entrance, ensuring convenience for both tenants and homeowners.  This immense bonus space is great for substantial additional income, an in-law suite or extensive living space. The large fenced backyard provides an ideal space for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or just relaxing equipped with a large swing set and two large sheds for additional outdoor storage.   The long driveway has spaces for two vehicles plus ample street parking.   Excellent location - only a 4 minute drive to the Glenmont Metro Station, 5 to the Wheaton Metro Station/Mall, 12 minutes to Rockville Town Center, 13 minutes to NIH, 15 minutes to downtown Bethesda. Truly a wonderful property!
